item.title: CVE-2023-22523|2023-12-06T15:30:00.483Z -- atlassian -- assets%20discovery%20cloud
item.description: This vulnerability, if exploited, allows an attacker to perform privileged RCE (Remote Code Execution) on machines with the Assets Discovery agent installed. The vulnerability exists between the Assets Discovery application (formerly known as Insight Discovery) and the Assets Discovery agent.
